## ðŸ”Œ Pairing with the existing UI

Your mock UI already has tabs for PayPal and Crypto. Point the **Pay** button to `POST /pay`:

* If `rail === 'paypal'` â†’ redirect to `response.redirect`
* If `rail === 'evm'` â†’ open WalletConnect/MetaMask with the returned `{ chainId, to, data, value }`

Example wallet call (client):

```ts
// EIP-155 request
await window.ethereum.request({
  method: 'eth_sendTransaction',
  params: [{
    from: userAddress,
    to: payload.to,
    data: payload.data,
    value: payload.value
  }]
});
```

